<p><span class="anchor" id="p43"></span>انقبض وَفُلَانًا عاتبه<a href="#p43" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p44"></span><span class="c2">(المرعز)</span> الزغب الَّذِي تَحت شعر العنز<a href="#p44" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
